name: ONLY GOD CAN JUDGE ME by René Mäkelä #1/1
description:
# Only God can judge me, unique edition #1/1
The aim of this work is to create a contrast between the icons of popular culture (2pac and Basquiat's crown) and the baroque and renaissance styles, as well as to pay homage to the old European masters: Velázquez, Caravaggio, Rembrant, Rubens.... I present 2pac as an angel in reference to his song *'Only God can judge me'*.

attributes.trait_type: 25th anniversary of the death of Tupac Amaru Shakur
